  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to analyze biopsied tissue samples for changes in cells and
      genes involved in Barrett's Esophagus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with a history of Barrett's esophagus who are scheduled for a routine endoscopy will
      have an additional biopsy taken for genetic testing.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
